children.subject: Thanks for pointing that out, not sure why they don't offer it. Do you recommend any easy upper division course?
CS 168 is not being offered next semester: https://www2.eecs.berkeley.edu/Scheduling/CS/schedule-draft.html

history.content:
61C + 170 is hard but doable, adding 16B would create a very high workload but it’s up to you, 61C and 16B are both more technical while 170 is all theoretical... since that’s only 12 units, I would suggest either taking a decal or a breadth class for the 13th+ unit, and not another upper div, but if you insist, data 100 is relatively low workload :) 

______________________________________
